msgid "# Belt of Dwarvenkind _Wondrous item, rare (requires attunement)_"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/belt_of_dwarvenkind.md:8
msgid "While wearing this belt, you gain the following benefits:"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/belt_of_dwarvenkind.md:11
msgid "Your Constitution score increases by 2, to a maximum of 20."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/belt_of_dwarvenkind.md:11
msgid ""
"You have advantage on Charisma (Persuasion) checks made to interact with "
"dwarves."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/belt_of_dwarvenkind.md:14
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"In addition, while attuned to the belt, you have a 50 percent chance each "
"day at dawn of growing a full beard if you're capable of growing one, or a "
"visibly thicker beard if you already have one.    \n"
"If you aren't a dwarf, you gain the following additional benefits while "
"wearing the belt:\n"
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/belt_of_dwarvenkind.md:17
msgid ""
"You have advantage on saving throws against poison, and you have resistance "
"against poison damage."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/belt_of_dwarvenkind.md:17
msgid "You have darkvision out to a range of 60 feet."
msgstr ""

#. type: Bullet: '* '
#: sources/gamemaster_rules/magic_items/belt_of_dwarvenkind.md:17
msgid "You can speak, read, and write Dwarvish."
msgstr ""
